{"tid":965720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"41J 正文！正宮捉姦一個打兩個　捏爆老公下體「一帶一路」","createTime":"2019-01-02T09:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T09:28:07.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9e25c8ede94e2b01d71000b1a2f5dd215f10d9","tid":965720,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"據英國《鏡報》報導，這名正宮當街捉到了老公和小三卡蘿(Carol)幽會，但這位正宮河東獅吼，個性剽悍，當場質問卡蘿。卡蘿一直宣稱「我不知道他已婚」，但正宮不接受這個說法，反罵小三：「你再說謊啊，你會看不出來有人在照顧他啊！」、「你這個賤人，我要教訓你！」之後正宮開始對卡蘿巴頭。<br />\n老公一度要介入兩人紛爭，要當和事佬，但正宮實在太強大，瞬間轉過頭來直接打爆老公的大頭，隨後又捏爆老公下體「小頭」，讓老公痛不欲生，甚至一路拽著老公的陰莖「一帶一路」又走又跑。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190102/1493330/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190102%2F1493330%2F&d=WzviOvFWrGNRmPFYDsyrJW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bf9857dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190102%2F1493330%2F&h=8ceecdf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190102/1493330/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190102/640_3a01094c7e19b5c1514b7fcc5ccd8529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190102%2F640_3a01094c7e19b5c1514b7fcc5ccd8529.jpg&h=21b7ac89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190102/640_3777dc6f22fb027d8de9617e1c927c12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190102%2F640_3777dc6f22fb027d8de9617e1c927c12.jpg&h=d4be630b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190102/640_2229c862d697dddf6358f6c560ad2302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190102%